  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with trisomy 21 are in greater danger of developing caries. It has been hypothesized
      that adding silver nanoparticles to fluor varnishes could promote remineralization of the
      teeth. A split-plot randomized controlled trial will be performed to address this question.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
